      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Anyway, the thieves go away with six vehicles: a black 2020 Dodge Durango SRT, black 2017 Jeep Grand Cherokee SRT, red 2014 Jeep Grand Cherokee SRT, red 2020 Dodge Charger Scat Pack, red 2018 Dodge Challenger R/T, and black 2015 Dodge Challenger Hellcat.",
