            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "According to the dealership owner, Al Saad, the six vehicles are worth about $50,000 each. That means he took a $300,000 hit in no time. We’re not saying those valuations are correct, but that’s what he told the local news, so if you think he’s wrong take it up with him.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "image",
        "src": "__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2020/10/Motorious---6--21.jpg",
        "width": 1920,
        "height": 1080,
        "caption": "photo credit: Fiat Chrysler Automobiles"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Lately, some people flippantly say when cars are destroyed or stolen, dealerships and even private citizens aren’t really inconvenienced because everything is ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "covered by insurance",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "__GHOST_URL__/articles/news/riots-and-car-insurance/",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". We question if these people have ever made an insurance claim or even carry insurance. Saad told the local news he really doesn’t want to file a claim for $300,000 in losses, likely because his premium will shoot up, eating into profits which no doubt have taken a hit during these turbulent, shutdown-filled times.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "At the moment there’s a $10,000 reward for anyone who provides information leading to the arrest of those responsible for the car thefts. We bet someone could really use that extra cash right now.",
